# Home K8s Cluster

## Pre-Requisites
```
brew install fluxcd/tap/flux
```

##  Flux

```
export GITHUB_TOKEN=<your-token>
flux bootstrap github \
  --owner=carsten-bo \
  --repository=k8s-home \
  --path=cluster \
  --personal
```
## 1Password

```
kubectl create secret generic operator.token.value --from-literal=token="<TOKEN>" --namespace=secrets-manager

kubectl create secret generic op-credentials --from-file=1password-credentials.json --namespace=secrets-manager

```
